# =================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# =================================================

# 1. Never commit .env files to version control
# 2. Use different API keys for development and production
# 3. Set strong JWT secrets (32+ characters, random)
# 4. Restrict CORS origins to your actual domains
# 5. Use HTTPS in production (never HTTP)
# 6. Consider using a secrets management service for production
# 7. Regularly rotate API keys and secrets
# 8. Monitor API usage and set appropriate rate limits

# =================================================
# GETTING YOUR HOSTFULLY CREDENTIALS
# =================================================

# 1. Log into your Hostfully account
# 2. Go to Settings > API Access
# 3. Generate an API key
# 4. Find your Agency UID in the account settings
# 5. Use the API version URL provided by Hostfully

